{"tid":1755986,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(公民黨帶動)  民主黨 樂意聘用抗爭者","createTime":"2019-11-26T00:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T04:07:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0705aba5a53d249b0c58cb53e335e55866391b","tid":1755986,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:26:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191126/s00002/1574707698083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191126%2Fs00002%2F1574707698083&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmSDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=3de024d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191126%2Fs00002%2F1574707698083&h=b8e2e10e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191126/s00002/1574707698083</a><br />\n<br />\n019年11月26日星期二<br />\n港聞一<br />\n民主黨願聘抗爭者 有當選者稱捐薪<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】反修例風波下，民主派在區議會選舉大勝。目前區議員薪金，連同酬酢開支等，每月合共約逾4萬元，有當選者稱會將部分薪津捐出，用以支援抗爭者。<strong>民主黨主席胡志偉表示，如抗爭者需要工作機會，「我們很樂意招募」，加上該黨將新增多個議辦，強調會積極跟進；公民黨主席梁家傑則稱會盡快開會討論坊間建議。</strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會約半年前通過區議員增加薪津項目，區議員月薪增至33,950元、非實報實銷雜項開支津貼為每月7690元；實報實銷開支則包括每月4.5萬元營運開支償還款額，即每年有103.7萬薪酬及津貼；另每屆有12萬元開設辦事處款額。<br />\n區議員每年薪津逾百萬<br />\n<br />\n出戰東涌南、擊敗民建聯周浩鼎的王進洋，昨日當選後公開承諾，「第一時間捐了人工先」，明言會每月捐出最少1.3萬元薪金，盼能直接支援抗爭者，但仍在思考捐款模式，包括考慮聯同其他候任區議員一同捐款。<br />\n<br />\n民主派政黨方面，胡志偉昨表示該黨有加入「良心僱主」平台，而若有抗爭者需要工作崗位，會很樂意招募，加上未來將新增不少議辦，定會積極跟進。至於會否作捐薪等資源承諾，他稱牽涉到區議員的生活需要，但若黨員能出任區議會主席或副主席，或會有額外酬金，會要求考慮如何利用有關資源支援運動所需。<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑稱，該黨執委會已決定盡快邀請所有候任區議員出席「擴大會議」，並於會上討論坊間種種建議。該黨立法會議員譚文豪稱，不少當選者都曾向他表達冀能支援抗爭者，但因昨日尚未與所有區議員會面，故暫未清晰整體意向。<br />\n<br />\n（反修例風暴）"},{"pid":"6579589161f4dc09597f0d85ef6d305a58cb8e1f","tid":1755986,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:27:32.000Z","msg":"之前<br />\n<br />\n公民黨表示會聘請抗爭者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1754692/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1754692/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"10a3026a496ad9cc64c91efc6e6db1858b3835d0","tid":1755986,"uid":304856,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:27:33.000Z","msg":"百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d18ff8ee8bb1769ce0dd89a1862a04dd33fc6e5","tid":1755986,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10a3026a496ad9cc64c91efc6e6db1858b3835d0","tid":1755986,"uid":304856,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:27:33.000Z","msg":"百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c8d7df5a0da7cd18bb9fb89f88dcaf51d341dd","tid":1755986,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cef88e646cdccae00f8a8ec6abd661a5b78cd6d","tid":1755986,"uid":162327,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"王進洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰日係東涌見你官仔骨骨咁 估唔到咁大手筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時整幅連儂牆出嚟啊？"},{"pid":"85b51f4578b602b46265ffa784bd42c1d4ea40f6","tid":1755986,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit